snippet.title: Calcium Contract - Eternal Harvest
snippet.description:
New game mode available now as a free update!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2427960/Calcium_Contract/

Eternal Harvest is a free update adding a new way of experiencing Calcium Contract.
It's an intense score-attack mode in procedurally generated levels that continue changing while you play, with increasing difficulty and new risk & reward mechanics.
Test your skills against your friends or the world in a global leaderboard or daily challenges.
